transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Executive: Haan mam aapne call kiya tha?
Customer: Kon Sushmita baat kar raha tha?
Executive: Ji ji ji ji.
Customer: Abhi just hui na meeting?
Executive: Ah mam ho gayi meeting ab mujhe ek cheez jaani hai aur Nazma Begum kon hai?
Customer: Nahi pata wohi toh bata rahi hu.
Executive: Mam aap toh unse hi call kar dete ho problem yeh hai.
Customer: Maine kab call kiya tha? Iske number pe call kiya hai na?
Executive: Nahi is number pe nahi aapne dusre number pe call kiya hai.
Customer: Mujhe samajh mein nahi aa raha aapka jo number hai na usse 990044687.
Customer: Nahi. Mai ek baar check karwa leti hu phir aap.
Executive: Theek hai.
summary:

- Wants to know who Nazma Begum is.

- Customer says executive called on another number.



Resolution:

- Executive will check the number.
